      "noSpeechProb": 0.008655291981995106
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start": 48.51,
      "end": 55.94,
      "text": "他們就應該堅持不斷交易",
      "avgLogprob": -0.1671381172252028,
      "noSpeechProb": 0.008655291981995106
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start": 55.94,
      "end": 59.54,
      "text": "但是,如果他們能夠進行交易並管理得大",
      "avgLogprob": -0.1671381172252028,
      "noSpeechProb": 0.008655291981995106
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start": 59.54,
      "end": 61.38,
      "text": "那就繼續進行交易吧",
      "avgLogprob": -0.1671381172252028,
      "noSpeechProb": 0.008655291981995106
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start": 61.38,
      "end": 65.22,
      "text": "我曾用過這樣一個形象,一個小人深出他的手臂",
